<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Cloud Systems</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: "Segoe UI", system-ui, sans-serif; background: #fff; color: #1a1a1a; }
    header { background: #0078d4; color: #fff; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; }
    header h1 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .03em; }

    main {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 3rem auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
    @media (max-width: 680px) {
      main { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    }

    /* Left: info table */
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
    tr { border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; }
    tr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    td { padding: .6rem 0; font-size: .9rem; vertical-align: top; }
    td:first-child { color: #605e5c; width: 42%; }
    td:last-child { color: #1a1a1a; font-weight: 500; }
    .label { font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .1em; color: #0078d4; padding-top: 1.5rem; padding-bottom: .25rem; }

    /* Right: about + visitor */
    .right { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; }

    .card-label {
      font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .1em; color: #0078d4; margin-bottom: .75rem;
    }

    .highlights { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .6rem; }
    .highlights li {
      font-size: .85rem; color: #3a3a3a; line-height: 1.5;
      padding-left: 1rem; position: relative;
    }
    .highlights li::before {
      content: "→"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #0078d4; font-weight: 700;
    }

    .visitor-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
    .visitor-table tr { border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; }
    .visitor-table tr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .visitor-table td { padding: .5rem 0; font-size: .85rem; vertical-align: top; }
    .visitor-table td:first-child { color: #605e5c; width: 42%; }
    .visitor-table td:last-child { color: #1a1a1a; font-weight: 500; font-family: monospace; font-size: .8rem; word-break: break-all; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Cloud Systems</h1>
  </header>
  <main>

    <!-- Left column: infrastructure facts -->
    <div>
      <table>
        <tr><td class="label" colspan="2">Host</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Domain</td><td>{{ app_domain }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Region</td><td>Azure South Central US</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Protocol</td><td>HTTP/2, TLS 1.2/1.3</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Certificate</td><td>Let's Encrypt (auto-renewing)</td></tr>

        <tr><td class="label" colspan="2">Stack</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Web server</td><td>nginx</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Database</td><td>MariaDB</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Provisioning</td><td>Terraform</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Configuration</td><td>Ansible</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Secrets</td><td>Ansible Vault</td></tr>
        <tr><td>State</td><td>Azure Blob Storage</td></tr>

        <tr><td class="label" colspan="2">Network</td></tr>
        <tr><td>App subnet</td><td>10.0.1.0/24 — public</td></tr>
        <tr><td>DB subnet</td><td>10.0.2.0/24 — private</td></tr>
        <tr><td>DB access</td><td>App subnet only</td></tr>
        <tr><td>SSH</td><td>DB reachable via bastion only</td></tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <!-- Right column: about + live visitor info -->
    <div class="right">

      <div>
        <div class="card-label">About this project</div>
        <ul class="highlights">
          <li>Fully automated two-tier deployment — one <code>terraform apply</code> provisions the network, VMs, and NSGs; one <code>ansible-playbook</code> configures everything.</li>
          <li>Self-healing: Terraform writes the live public IP into Ansible's inventory and group vars on every apply, so the stack always converges to the correct state automatically.</li>
          <li>Zero-trust network segmentation — the database is unreachable from the internet; only the app subnet can connect on port 3306.</li>
          <li>Secrets never touch disk in plaintext — DB credentials are encrypted at rest with Ansible Vault and the Terraform state is stored remotely in Azure Blob Storage.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="card-label">Your session</div>
        <table class="visitor-table">
          <tr><td>Browser</td><td id="v-browser">—</td></tr>
          <tr><td>OS</td><td id="v-os">—</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Language</td><td id="v-lang">—</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Screen</td><td id="v-screen">—</td></tr>
          <tr><td>User agent</td><td id="v-ua">—</td></tr>
        </table>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>

  <script src="/session.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
